Dan DOSS, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 11735. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit Dec. 12, 1946. Dan Doss, of Leavenworth, Kan., for appellant, in pro. per. Malcolm E. Lafargue, U. S. Atty., of Shreveport, La., for appellee.

Before HUTCHESON, McCORD, and LEE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On authority of Morgan v. Devine, 237 U.S. 632, 35 S.Ct. 712, 59 L.Ed. 1153, the judgment, 66 F.Supp. 243, is affirmed.
